            "title": "盤中速報 - 一詮(2486)大跌9.56%，報132.5元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>一詮(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2486:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2486\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2486-TW</a>)31日13:02股價下跌14元，報132.5元，跌幅9.56%，成交1,272張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>一詮(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2486:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2486\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2486-TW</a>)所屬產業為光電業，主要業務為LED及SMD導線架。直下式電視背光模組、散熱片及IC導線架。其他電子零組件。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲2.45%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌0.62%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+571 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+469 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：+87 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+15 張</li> <li>融資增減：-855 張</li> <li>融券增減：+14 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
